description: The country's election has put Belarus back into the headlines but what do you know about the country?
title: Belarus: Five things you may not know about the country
title_page: Belarus: Five things you may not know about the country - BBC News
maintext: "My soul is definitely Belarusian and whatever happens and wherever I am, my roots will always be here," she told the Minsk Herald. "I grew up in Belarus and my parents still live here, besides my character was formed here. When I come to Belarus, I come to my home country."
